Nested Cats Extension
------------------------------------

Version: 2.0 beta
Author: Andrey Lubinov (andrey.lubinov@gmail.com)
Build Date: 4th March 2010


[INSTALLATION]

1. Upload the 'nestedcats' folder in this archive to your Symphony 'extensions' folder.

2. Enable it by selecting the "Nested Cats", choose Enable from the with-selected menu, then click Apply.


[USAGE]
- 1. Go to the Categories/Overview and add some categories.
  2. Append "Nested Cats" field to your section.
  3. Append "Nested Cats" Data Source to your page (optional).

- See Data Source's about for example XML and possible XSL template.

